snippet.title: Resident Evil (Chris + Jill Playthrough) | GBC Prototype | Longplay | Walkthrough #1 [4Kp60]
snippet.description:
https://twitter.com/LongplayU

Rating: 4/5

Positives
- Graphics
- Gameplay
- Music
- Cutscenes
- Has a playthrough for both Chris and Jill

Mediocre
-  Controls (Yeah can be hard to control character but it's not a big deal because there aren't many enemies)
- Music

Negatives
- Not many weapons, enemies, or any boss fights
- Unfinished (I know it was never finished or released but wish there was an ending)
